description: Are you ready for a Wok on the wild side? The street food revolution is going strong in Arizona, and Wok Sticks is joining in with a selection of delectable cuisine from nations like China, Japan, Korea, and more. With their Gyoza, Kung Pao Chicken, California Rolls, and more, they've got something perfect for any appetite. Try the East valley's finest new food truck today, and experience the incomparable Wok Sticks!
name: Wok Sticks
